docs.snippet: TAMPA, Fla., Jan. 20 (AP)-- Betsy Rawls staved off a strong challenge by Fay Crocker of Uruguay today to win the Tampa women's open golf tournament for the second straight year. The winning margin was one stroke.
docs.lead_paragraph: TAMPA, Fla., Jan. 20 (AP)-- Betsy Rawls staved off a strong challenge by Fay Crocker of Uruguay today to win the Tampa women's open golf tournament for the second straight year. The winning margin was one stroke.
